{"tid":1180803,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"長期耳鳴討論區","createTime":"2019-06-01T06:18:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T17:20:40.000Z","uid":8701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8fcfd3a6205d1ed84b29c9a50b4a4ab6ce14faf7","tid":1180803,"uid":8701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T06:18:02.000Z","msg":"事源大半年前有一次大感冒<br />\n鼻水倒流引致中耳發炎<br />\n當然有又耳塞又耳痛<br />\n<br />\n好返之後就開始有耳鳴聲 (24小時高頻vvvv聲)<br />\n精神狀態好就會細聲啲<br />\n但一攰就會V得勁好多<br />\n有時太太太攰，直頭會發岀幾下既轟轟聲<br />\n<br />\n夜晚訓教就基本上一定聽到V聲<br />\n<br />\n照過MRI , 睇過內窺鏡都話無發現咩問題<br />\n叫我接受現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但到依家我大力搖個頭，係feel到有啲液體係耳仔到浪下浪下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴打有類似問題，而又好返架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac4ae9b7ea805a4b04ef8fdc1b59433c26bdca23","tid":1180803,"uid":8701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:56:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b823e049995c87d590945755c525fd8e12b9b0c1","tid":1180803,"uid":71058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:57:48.000Z","msg":"我都有耳鳴問題，有可能係聽覺神經退化，習慣啦唯有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710c62175656cbea8ca80cbbcdede683e9b07240","tid":1180803,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T08:03:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我又係病完之後有"},{"pid":"395cfc19e0107662e0b0dad92607d25e73cffd29","tid":1180803,"uid":8548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T08:21:39.000Z","msg":"我係夜晚好靜嘅時候就有<br />\n<br />\n通常都係瞓覺前攤喺張床嗰陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd343a34d0a8ddfc994f5dac0470e3b771994a6e","tid":1180803,"uid":8701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b823e049995c87d590945755c5